Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\blur3}{\3c&H1709C8&}Wear our favorite clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:57.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}{\3c&H1709C8&}We are at no doubt human beings
